OL,3,CThe ex-sofa surfer hoping to help
OL,4,Cmarginalised communities find housing
OL,6,FA former sofa surfer from London who
OL,7,Fturned his life around to support
OL,8,Fpeople from marginalised communities
OL,9,Fat risk of homelessness is hoping to
OL,10,Fbring his work to Bristol.
OL,12,FPeter Merrifield runs Support When It
OL,13,FMatters Enterprise (SWIM), a community
OL,14,Finterest company which empowers people
OL,15,Ffrom African, Caribbean and dual
OL,16,Fheritage backgrounds to improve their
OL,17,Fhealth, mental wellbeing and quality
OL,18,Fof life.
