OL,3,CThe ex-sofa surfer hoping to help
OL,4,Cmarginalised communities find housing
OL,6,FNow, Peter plans to bring SWIM to
OL,7,FBristol to help people in those
OL,8,Fcommunities struggling to find
OL,9,Faccommodation.
OL,11,FPeter founded the social enterprise in
OL,12,F2019, after being motivated by his
OL,13,Fpersonal challenges with substance
OL,14,Fmisuse and recovery, as well as his
OL,15,Fheritage as a child of the Windrush
OL,16,Fgeneration.
