OL,3,CThe ex-sofa surfer hoping to help
OL,4,Cmarginalised communities find housing
OL,6,FSWIM was created from Peter's own
OL,7,Fexperience of sofa surfing, living in
OL,8,Fmakeshift accommodation and
OL,9,Fdifficulties in finding affordable,
OL,10,Fpermanent accommodation.
OL,12,FFrom an initial investment of just
OL,13,F#5,000 in 2020, SWIM now has a
OL,14,Fturnover of #2 million.
OL,16,FIn the past few years, SWIM has
OL,17,Fdeveloped a number of programmes
OL,18,Fincluding projects which help men and
OL,19,Fwomen who have been released from
OL,20,Fprison, as well as accommodation for
OL,21,Fthe homeless.
