OL,3,CThe ex-sofa surfer hoping to help
OL,4,Cmarginalised communities find housing
OL,6,FSpeaking to ITV News West Country,
OL,7,FPeter said: "A significant proportion
OL,8,Fof Black Africans in Bristol live in
OL,9,Fovercrowded or inadequate housing
OL,10,Fconditions.
OL,12,F"The 2021 census indicates that 43.3%
OL,13,Fof Black Africans live in households
OL,14,Fwith fewer bedrooms than required -
OL,15,Fcompared to 9.5% of the city's overall
OL,16,Fpopulation.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
