OL,3,CThe ex-sofa surfer hoping to help
OL,4,Cmarginalised communities find housing
OL,6,F"This highlights the critical need for
OL,7,Fhousing solutions. Such issues
OL,8,Fcontribute to other social and health
OL,9,Fproblems, such as increased stress,
OL,10,Fmental health and reduced
OL,11,Fopportunities."
OL,13,FPeter hopes SWIM can create a long-
OL,14,Flasting footprint in Bristol, using a
OL,15,Fsimilar model to the one proven to be
OL,16,Fsuccessful in London.
OL,18,FThe idea is to collaborate with local
OL,19,Fservices and charities to bring the
OL,20,Fsupport he wished he had to people.
