OL,3,CThe ex-sofa surfer hoping to help
OL,4,Cmarginalised communities find housing
OL,6,FPeter said: "We invite all
OL,7,Fstakeholders, including local
OL,8,Fauthorities, healthcare providers,
OL,9,Fcommunity organisations, and private
OL,10,Fdonors, to join us in this vital
OL,11,Finitiative.
OL,13,F"Together, we can make a lasting
OL,14,Fimpact on the lives of many
OL,15,Findividuals and their families."
